{"tid":2027043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果立會參選人冇以下任何一項政綱，我絕對唔會投佢：","createTime":"2020-05-21T09:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:21:56.000Z","uid":47021,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e6e1380ee30fb16274cf13d0253fc9fa0a1d5c","tid":2027043,"uid":47021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"1. 支持警隊嚴正執法，拘捕所有黑暴分子，如黑暴分子拒捕，可以使用最高武力shoot to kill<br />\n<br />\n2. 支持建立集中營，對黑暴分子再教育<br />\n<br />\n3. 由於黑暴分子大多為青年人，因此估計教育出問題，強烈要求所有學校（包括國際學校、大學）增加國民教育課，每日兩節共兩小時。中學生升讀大學時必須通過國安檢測，嚴防黑暴分子污染我國莘莘學子的愛國精神<br />\n<br />\n4. 所有在香港有業務的公司，均需受中國派駐人員規管，以防止外國勢力操控香港，資助反中亂港人員<br />\n<br />\n大家都係中國人，愛國嘅候選人起碼都要中一個啦係咪，否則就係支持黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪投依班假建制真黑暴候選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca88fc3d5e43a7a3c6c51a3f5bda54df7754348","tid":2027043,"uid":47021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:41:35.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2adef0aa72323ba414db8b844e4438cc86f0b94","tid":2027043,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"要求全港學生背誦毛主席語錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shoSHqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FshoSHqp.jpg&h=ea3f627b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 毛主席萬歲，萬歲，萬萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />🇨🇳🇨🇳"},{"pid":"d61f6530eaa6e3d2b6fa794e44af2cccc8c80fa1","tid":2027043,"uid":142233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"過左國安法 仲可唔可以咁講再9up la"},{"pid":"fb6dd8586bea45141025c64d6d2673c010f9fdfa","tid":2027043,"uid":117073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"今日人大已經向仲信選舉嗰班人證明立會戰線真係廢㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"